info.name: Dark YouTube Search Bar
info.description: Adds an unofficial dark theme to the YouTube search bar!
info.additionalInfo:
Changelog:
[10/31/22]
-Changed color of search results to match YouTube's new dark theme

[3/22/22]
-Changed color of the search results since YouTube changed the color of them on light theme
-Changed color of the "Remove" button to be consistent with Google's official dark theme
-Changed color of the new icons next to each search term

[2/11/22]
-Fixed bug in which highlighted search results would sometimes be in light theme
